@startuml
title Enricher - State Machine Diagram (TO BE)

[*] --> Input

Input --> Skipped : row missing OR upstream errors
Input --> ExecuteOps : valid row

ExecuteOps --> Failed : operation FAILED (policy=ERROR)
ExecuteOps --> NeedsResolve : operation NEEDS_RESOLVE (ambiguous/missing key)
ExecuteOps --> Enriched : operations completed

NeedsResolve --> StoreSecrets
Enriched --> StoreSecrets
Skipped --> Output

StoreSecrets --> Output : secrets stored OR skipped OR secret-store warning

Failed --> Output

Output --> [*]

note right of NeedsResolve
Enricher does NOT resolve identity.\nIt emits ResolveHint(s) in meta\nfor Resolver to act (pending_links / conflict / manual).
end note

note right of StoreSecrets
If secret_candidates exist:\n- require match_key\n- put_many into SecretStore\n- on error => ENRICH warning/error by policy
end note

@enduml
